snippet.title: Bathhouse Creatures | Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Bathhouse Creatures is a small and cozy management game about building up an old bathhouse, keeping animal guests happy, and watching your bathhouse grow to be the best it can be! 🐥♨️💖

Wishlist or play the Demo now on Steam!
